data.description: Are you looking for privacy?  Check out the 3D video on the virtual tour link of this One Owner, Open Floor Plan, All Electric 5 Bedrooms, 3 Baths  Reverse 1 1/2 story home in a cul-de-sac with Wooded Lot! Kitchen features Corian Counter tops, Birch Custom Cabinets, Pantry & Bamboo Floors! Master Bedroom suite Features Private Master Bath & Walk In Closet! 19 X 26 Storage Room in Basement. Roof is only 3 years old! Leaf Filter Gutter Guards installed  with transferrable warranty! All appliances stay including Washer & Dryer! 1 year old Electric Heat Pump Furnace & A/C! Home was constructed with exterior 2x6 framing providing great insulation!  There is plenty of extra bamboo flooring in the attic!  Storm shelter in basement. Radon Mitigation system installed 2018.
